	<!-- Notes from document:

	Aqua-planet : cloud response to an imposed uniform change in SST.

	Consistent with CFMIP requirements, add a uniform +4K to the zonally uniform SSTs of expt. 6.7a (which is the control for this run).

	-->

	<rationale> To explore the degree to which future climate states depend on the initial climate state (from 'A Summary of the CMIP5 Experiment Design' by Karl Taylor et al. 2008)</rationale>
	<why/>
	
